metadata.name: Friends
metadata.description:
We need friends. Everyone does. Some people dont think so. I was one of those on occasion. I have been in many different  "scenes" over the years. A few a bit hostile and jealous. Many quite supportive, but I have never quite experienced the level of love and support Web 3/NFT Community provides. I have found this extraordinary. 

This is a composite of elements rendered in 3d, AI components and post. It is a soft focus work that represents the serenity and support friends can mutually give to each other.
